title: Andr hook
description: Query the current contract owner

title: Includes address
description: Query if address is included

title: Code id
description: All code IDs for Andromeda contracts

title: Auction ids
description: Gets the auction ids for the given token.

title: Auction infos for address
description: Gets all of the auction infos for a given token address.

title: Auction state
description: Gets the auction state for the given auction id.

title: Bids
description: Gets the bids for the given auction id. Start_after starts indexing at 0.

title: Is closed
description: Returns true only if the auction has been cancelled, the token has been claimed, or the end time has expired

title: Latest auction state
description: Gets the latest auction state for the given token. This will either be the current auction if there is one in progress or the last completed one.

title: Get splitter config
description: The current config of the Splitter contract

title: All accounts
description: Only with "enumerable" extension Returns all accounts that have balances. Supports pagination. Return type: AllAccountsResponse.

title: All allowances
description: Only with "enumerable" extension (and "allowances") Returns all allowances this owner has approved. Supports pagination. Return type: AllAllowancesResponse.

title: Allowance
description: Only with "allowance" extension. Returns how much spender can use from owner account, 0 if unset. Return type: AllowanceResponse.

title: Balance
description: Returns the current balance of the given address, 0 if unset. Return type: BalanceResponse.

title: Download logo
description: Only with "marketing" extension Downloads the mbeded logo data (if stored on chain). Errors if no logo data ftored for this contract. Return type: DownloadLogoResponse.

title: Marketing info
description: Only with "marketing" extension Returns more metadata on the contract to display in the client: - description, logo, project url, etc. Return type: MarketingInfoResponse

title: Minter
description: Only with "mintable" extension. Returns who can mint and the hard cap on maximum tokens after minting. Return type: MinterResponse.

title: Token info
description: Returns metadata on the contract - name, decimals, supply, etc. Return type: TokenInfoResponse.

title: Sale
description: Sale info for a given asset

title: Token address
description: The address of the token being purchased

title: Config
description: Gets the config of the contract.

title: Staker
description: Returns a `StakerResponse` for the given staker. The pending rewards are updated to the present index.

title: Stakers
description: Returns a `Vec<StakerResponse>` for range of stakers. The pending rewards are updated to the present index for each staker.

title: State
description: Gets the state of the contract.

title: Timestamp
description: Queries the current timestamp.

title: All operators
description: Approvals for a given address (paginated)

title: All tokens

title: Approvals
description: Return approvals that a token has Return type: `ApprovalsResponse`

description: The current config of the contract

title: Nft info
